<%# ──────────────────────────── HERO ──────────────────────────── %>
<div class="lenders-hero">
  <div class="lenders-hero-inner">
    <span class="section-label" style="color: var(--color-steel);">Private Lending</span>
    <h1 class="heading-display" style="color: #fff; margin-top: 0.5rem;">Become a Lender</h1>
    <p style="max-width: 34rem; margin: 1.25rem auto 0; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.75;">
      Put your capital to work with real estate-backed hard money loans.
      Transparent terms, first-position liens, and a hands-on team
      managing every deal.
    </p>
    <div class="ctx-black" style="margin-top: 2rem; display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center;">
      <%= btn_tag "Schedule a Conversation", "https://calendly.com/anthony-socalkeys" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%# ──────────────────────────── VALUE PROP ──────────────────────────── %>
<div class="container-wide section">
  <div class="home-grid-2">
    <div>
      <span class="section-label">Why Lend With Us</span>
      <p class="heading-1">Your Capital.<br>Real Property.<br>Clear Terms.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="text-body">
        Traditional investments often lack transparency or tie up your money
        for years with little visibility into where it goes. Private lending
        through Linchpin Realty is different. Every dollar you deploy is
        secured by a tangible asset, real property, with clearly defined
        terms, timelines, and protections.
      </p>
      <p class="text-body" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
        We handle the sourcing, underwriting, servicing, and collection.
        You provide the capital. We provide the infrastructure and
        deal flow to keep it working.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%# ──────────────────────────── HOW IT WORKS ──────────────────────────── %>
<div style="background: var(--color-smoke); border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
  <div class="container-wide section">
    <span class="section-label">How It Works</span>
    <p class="heading-1" style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">Straightforward Structure</p>

    <div class="home-grid-3 loans-types-grid">
      <div class="card-elevated" style="padding: 2rem;">
        <div class="loans-step-number" style="font-size: 2rem;">01</div>
        <p class="heading-3" style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">We Source the Deal</p>
        <div class="divider" style="margin: 1rem 0;"></div>
        <p class="text-body">
          We identify and vet borrowers, evaluate properties, and structure
          loans with built-in protections. You see every deal before
          committing a dollar.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-elevated" style="padding: 2rem;">
        <div class="loans-step-number" style="font-size: 2rem;">02</div>
        <p class="heading-3" style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">You Fund the Loan</p>
        <div class="divider" style="margin: 1rem 0;"></div>
        <p class="text-body">
          Choose the deals that fit your criteria. Funds are secured by
          a recorded deed of trust on the property. First-position lien,
          every time.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-elevated" style="padding: 2rem;">
        <div class="loans-step-number" style="font-size: 2rem;">03</div>
        <p class="heading-3" style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">We Manage Everything</p>
        <div class="divider" style="margin: 1rem 0;"></div>
        <p class="text-body">
          Servicing, draw inspections, payment collection, and borrower
          communication. We handle the day-to-day so you do not have to.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%# ──────────────────────────── WHAT YOU GET ──────────────────────────── %>
<div class="container-wide section">
  <span class="section-label">What You Get</span>

  <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 2rem;" class="lenders-benefits-grid">
    <div class="card" style="padding: 2rem;">
      <p class="heading-3">First-Position Liens</p>
      <p class="text-body" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
        Every loan is secured by a first-position deed of trust on the
        underlying property. Your capital is backed by a real, tangible asset.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="padding: 2rem;">
      <p class="heading-3">Full Transparency</p>
      <p class="text-body" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
        You receive complete loan documentation: appraisals, title reports,
        borrower details, and project scope. All before funding any deal.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="padding: 2rem;">
      <p class="heading-3">Defined Terms</p>
      <p class="text-body" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
        Interest rates, loan duration, and payment schedule are established
        up front. No ambiguity, no moving targets.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="padding: 2rem;">
      <p class="heading-3">Hands-Off Management</p>
      <p class="text-body" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
        We handle borrower relations, draw inspections, and payment
        processing. You stay informed without having to manage the details.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%# ──────────────────────────── WHO THIS IS FOR ──────────────────────────── %>
<div style="background: #000;">
  <div class="container-wide ctx-black" style="padding-top: 4rem; padding-bottom: 4rem;">
    <div class="home-grid-2">
      <div>
        <span class="section-label" style="color: var(--color-steel);">Is This Right for You</span>
        <p class="heading-1" style="color: #fff;">Built for Serious Capital</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); line-height: 1.75; font-size: 0.9375rem;">
          Private lending is not for everyone. It works best for individuals
          or entities with available capital looking for an alternative to
          traditional fixed-income products. People who value asset-backed
          security, defined timelines, and direct involvement in where their
          money goes.
        </p>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); line-height: 1.75; font-size: 0.9375rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
          If that sounds like you, let us have a conversation.
        </p>
        <div style="margin-top: 2rem;">
          <%= btn_tag "Schedule a Call", "https://calendly.com/anthony-socalkeys" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%# ──────────────────────────── CTA ──────────────────────────── %>
<div style="background: var(--color-navy);">
  <div class="container-wide ctx-navy" style="padding-top: 4rem; padding-bottom: 4rem; text-align: center;">
    <div style="max-width: 36rem; margin: 0 auto;">
      <p class="heading-1" style="color: white;">Ready to Deploy Capital?</p>
      <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-top: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; font-size: 0.9375rem;">
        No pitch deck, no pressure. Just a conversation about
        how private lending works and whether it fits your goals.
      </p>
      <div style="margin-top: 2rem; display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center;">
        <%= btn_tag "Schedule a Call", "https://calendly.com/anthony-socalkeys" %>
        <%= btn_tag "Email Us", "mailto:anthony@linchpinrealty.com" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%# ──────────────────────────── RELATED ARTICLES ──────────────────────────── %>
<% if @lender_blogs.any? %>
  <div class="container-wide section">
    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      <div>
        <span class="section-label" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">From the Knowledge Base</span>
        <p class="heading-1">Lending Resources</p>
      </div>
      <%= btn_tag "View All Articles", knowledge_index_path(category: "lenders") %>
    </div>
    <div class="knowledge-grid">
      <% @lender_blogs.each do |blog| %>
        <%= render "shared/blogs/blog_card", blog: blog %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
<% end %>
